{"tid":374589,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【IT人悲歌】路透：AXA本港裁250人 鏟起成個資訊科技部！","createTime":"2017-08-26T00:45:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-27T10:35:08.000Z","uid":17738,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5e127353777aa773faa63a6bf3a4c984dd648a66","tid":374589,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T00:45:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170825/large/1503664171_9889.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170825%2Flarge%2F1503664171_9889.jpg&h=bd27628e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【IT人悲歌】路透：AXA本港裁250人 鏟起成個資訊科技部！<br />\n<br />\n即時財經  2017-08-25 20:29:41 HKT\t <br />\n         <br />\n<br />\n【新增內容】<br />\n<br />\n又有機構裁減資訊科技（IT）員工！《路透社》引述兩名消息人士報道，保險公司AXA安盛在港裁250人，全部均是IT員工，原因是削減成本，而香港原本是AXA亞洲區的IT總部。<br />\n<br />\n裁員行動在本周四發生，AXA並同時移師至菲律賓馬尼拉及馬來西亞吉隆坡，在兩處設立資訊科技中心，分別聘請300人及110人，並形容在這些地區設立IT部是「在可負擔的成本上增強部門效能」。<br />\n<br />\nAXA發言人並無確認或否認裁員一事，僅指出AXA恒常地審視業務，以提升產品種類及服務，並於亞洲建立科技平台，致力提升科技水平及效能，中間或會牽涉部分區域的人手重整。<br />\n<br />\n資訊科技商會榮譽會長方保僑指出，不少企業因應減省成本，加上香港人工貴，租金貴，故此一些工序由其他地區取代，不過他認為，大企業在裁員前，必須要慎重考慮是否有其他安排，例如內部轉職，否則對其形象並不好。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今年IT人被企業開刀屬等閒事，例如國泰航空今年5月裁190名經理級以上員工，IT部是重災區，人數多達77人，主要是削減成本考慮。滙豐今年3月有逾百名IT員工收「大信封」，當時發言人回應指，削減成本為該行策略一部份，以確保競爭力及維持運作效率。<br />\n<br />\nAXA亦於2014年以26億元作價，將香港強積金業務轉售予美國信安，不過當時並未有牽涉裁員。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57128347&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170825\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57128347%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170825&d=zTAs14K9fH2hhD9loB0xJO9M5Ue6CDmcYDZznX2R1Ws%3D&h=91c12a3b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57128347%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170825&h=065e9153\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57128347&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170825</a><br />\n<br />\n// @老貓再世"},{"pid":"626cec731692d794939fefec98881c45b944f32f","tid":374589,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T04:32:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"746e6776d0ec2eda48b739aa518ab0c0b4e5b535","tid":374589,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T04:36:24.000Z","msg":"IT = high pay <br />\n<br />\nAsk 蓋清 for detail"},{"pid":"4bbe9d1ff5f4894cb948ca52f2b4af5837aac513","tid":374589,"uid":98317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T04:46:36.000Z","msg":"Ive civil 更稱心<br />\n年年見到成班on9仔走去讀ive 真係笑"},{"pid":"34ba71f9fcdaed199b06e45fd7c0341027699a19","tid":374589,"uid":98317,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T04:57:31.000Z","msg":"正確決定。真係睇唔到香港IT人有乜優勢，平唔夠東南亞同大陸平，精又唔夠歐美精"},{"pid":"f44fdfc1890803b7f66a428fc82cec59e1b3ff73","tid":374589,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T04:58:20.000Z","msg":"好心其他 it 職員都一齊辭職啦"},{"pid":"ffe309c6ee3af7fd39b115482f6ff6e283600fe2","tid":374589,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T05:07:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好心其他 it 職員都一齊辭職啦</blockquote><br />\n應該淨返d support仔幫人駁lan線"},{"pid":"1d65fea7ea272590da85ab8f67dc8d7dbd7eb06f","tid":374589,"uid":121580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T05:27:57.000Z","msg":"做it慘過做廁紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8789d3e04776ebbabf13545befc08579f49a1fef","tid":374589,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T14:55: